headline: Medtronic Chairman and CEO Geoff Martha to speak at J.P. Morgan healthcare conference
summary: Medtronic plc (NYSE:MDT), a global leader in healthcare technology, today announced it will participate in the 43rd annual J.P. Morgan healthcare conference on Monday, January 13, 2025.
